IR assignment files:


>>corpus folder
contains 768 files about top 1000 articles from wikipedia

1.token.py (to tokenize the files)
2.stemmer.c (to stem the file)
3.Gui.java (file to create graphical interface and this calls InvertedIndex.java)
4.InvertedIndex.java (to buildindex, to search the index)

To compile
2.cc stemmer.c  -o stemmer
3&4. javac Gui.java InvertedIndex.java

To run
1.python token.py
2. ./stemmer
3. java Gui

Instructions:

Enter the query in the text field in the java applet created and click "search" button. The search results will be displayed the text are below it.
